        <p>
            1) Show the B2B Form: on the main page, you can "<strong><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">Request a Quote</font></strong>"
        </p>
        <p>This customized form will create an opportunity in the CRM, with the right information, and the requirement.</p>
        <p>
            2) Visit the B2C Shop on the website: show variants and
            <strong>
                <font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">select other colors on Sofa</font>
